data.description: Don't miss this lovely Broadlands Townhome with 2 primary bedrooms, one on the main level and the other on the upper level. Lightly lived in and well taken care, this wonderful home is filled with natural light, big windows and high ceilings. Enjoy cozy evenings in your living room w/ gas fireplace and formal dining room with friends & family. Spacious eat-in kitchen is equipped with plenty of cabinets, counter and storage space; it also has a built in desk for a great catch- all for mail and important documents. The main floor powder room and laundry room complete the main level. Head upstairs to find the cheerful 2nd primary bedroom, bathroom and loft which would make a nice home office, library, hobby room or additional bedroom. The full basement is a blank canvas ready for you to finish as you wish. Enjoy morning coffee on your private patio! The Broadlands is a friendly & desirable community connected by parks, recreational amenities, trails, Plaster Reservoir, schools, club house, pool and an 18-hole championship golf course. Walking distance to Paul Derda rec center, Broomfield Commons park & open space. Just minutes to shopping, restaurants, pubs and cafes. Easy access to I-25, E-470 & HWY 7, 20 mins to Denver & Boulder. If viewing on the Zillow site, please scroll down to " Facts & Features" and click "Virtual Tour" to see more.
